            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your<strong> meat-free chick'n </strong>with the <strong>ground coriander</strong>, 1/3 of your<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><strong>garam masala </strong>(save the rest for later!) and a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>in a large bowl – this is your <strong>seasoned meat-free chick'n</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1635260054828-x200.jpg",
