          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1635260054828-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with a drizzle of<strong> vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>seasoned</strong> <strong>meat-free</strong> <strong>chick'n</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until warmed through and starting to brown</p><p>Once done, transfer the<strong> browned meat-free chick'n</strong> to a plate and reserve the pan</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1635260062208-x200.jpg",
