      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Peel and finely dice your <strong>brown</strong> <strong>onion[s]</strong></p><p>Return the reserved pan to a medium heat with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>butter</strong></p><p>Once the butter has melted, add the <strong>diced onion</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 5 min or until softened and starting to caramelise</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1635260067034-x200.jpg",
