            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the sauce has thickened, remove the pan from the heat and stir in your <strong>clotted cream </strong>– this is your<strong> meat-free butter chick'n</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
